  "plan": "Create an instrumented integer encoder (`enc_int_dbg.c`) and an instrumented decoder (`dec_int_dbg.c`) for `get_integer(9,0)` value 7. Run both, then compare the first lines of their traces. The encoder should print state after each `put_bit`; the decoder already prints state after each `get_bit`. This isolates the exact first divergence in the arithmetic coder state.",
